---
title: Spiced Fig , Chicken Breast Tenders and Golden Raisin-Rice Bowls with Protein Shreds and Creamy Shirazi Salad
description: Driven by earthy shawarma spices, this meal packs a 1-2 punch like no other. Fragrant golden turmeric rice and a creamy yogurt-sauce drizzle are the ultimate accompaniment to these sticky glazed plant-based protein shreds and chicken tenders.
